	   <tr><td colspan=2>what are you smoking? And did you bother to read all the posts here? The guy that submitted this item said it is only equipable in the range slot, which means you get the AC. This piece is best suited for a SK, although I keep it on my wizard at present but may eventually end up on my SK. <br><br>Getting the extra INT in the range slot makes it that much easier to replace other items that have higher +manna bonus than a Dusty Ball or other items. And the price is certainly not out of line either. After having read everything and talking to people in-game, there is no way I part with this baby unless someone makes a really insane offer.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
